  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK614">
<l>tāḷāṇmai yillātāṉ vēḷāṇmai pēṭikai </l>
<l>vāḷāṇmai pōlak keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The liberality of him, who does not labour, will fail, like the manliness of a hermaphrodite, who has a sword in its hand.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
